                    <p>
                        Experience the art's essence in all its splendor at ArtCodeCollective. Our carefully curated collection showcases boundary-breaking masterpieces, inviting you to enjoy the fascinating beauty that art has to offer. Immerse yourself in captivating strokes, vibrant colors, and thought-provoking concepts that touch the soul. 
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100">
